reviewText: Got this collection and finally watched Jane Eyre last week - it is the BEST JANE EYRE we have EVER SEEN, absolutely magnificent. This evening we began the Masterpiece Theatre's "WUTHERING HEIGHTS" and were disappointed to discover that it is VERY POORLY CAPTIONED - they left off dialogue of some characters, other captions are poorly done with words interspersed with non-words. So we are VERY DISAPPOINTED in this and there are NO SUBTITLES to switch to. We will see about the remaining 2 movies in the set.
summary: Warning: The Wuthering Heights is Poorly Captioned
